360
00:27:57,120 --> 00:27:58,440
Guy. Guy.

361
00:27:59,600 --> 00:28:01,680
- That's naughty.
- Is he going onto the stage?

362
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:03,760
Excuse me! I'm sorry.

363
00:28:07,760 --> 00:28:10,080
