365
00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:20,160
<i>♪ I want to break free ♪</i>

366
00:28:21,640 --> 00:28:24,040
<i>♪ I want to break free from your lies ♪</i>

367
00:28:24,040 --> 00:28:26,120
<i>♪ You're so self-satisfied ♪</i>

368
00:28:26,120 --> 00:28:28,560
<i>♪ I don't need you ♪</i>

