403
00:31:58,840 --> 00:32:00,600
It's meant to go under here.

404
00:32:01,560 --> 00:32:02,400
And it hasn't.

405
00:32:02,400 --> 00:32:03,920
That's it. Right about...

406
00:32:04,720 --> 00:32:05,600
Stop that.

407
00:32:06,280 --> 00:32:07,120
No.

