413
00:35:24,000 --> 00:35:27,240
- Yes, here I still am.
- No breakfast?

414
00:35:28,360 --> 00:35:29,320
Wasn't hungry.

415
00:35:30,080 --> 00:35:31,120
Not like you.

416
00:35:49,320 --> 00:35:50,200
How was Harry?

417
00:35:50,200 --> 00:35:51,880
