502
00:41:31,200 --> 00:41:34,720
- Not sure I like who you've been.
- Can you stop bickering? I beg you.

503
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:38,360
<i>How was supper?</i>

504
00:41:38,360 --> 00:41:40,920
